  "text": "ipRGCs (Sakai et al., 1986; [CITATION_1] . Last, ipRGCs could signal to DACs polysynaptically through multiple interneurons, although our data ruled out the involvement of ipRGC-coupled spiking amacrine cells (Reifler et al., 2015) .",
